title: A.J. Green Injury, Steelers hype with Bryant McFadden (Football 7/30)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and Bryant McFadden break down the latest news and notes from around the NFL, including the A.J. Green injury (2:00), whether Cincy could think about trading him down the road and what they would get (10:00), John Harbaugh talking Lamar Jackson's rushing attempts (12:30), B Mac's experience at Steelers training camp (19:00), Golden Tate's suspension (31:30), Mike Daniels signing with the Lions (35:45), Bobby Wagner signing a new deal with the Seahawks (38:00), Zeke Elliott's status (44:45) and B Mac's upcoming trip to the Jets and interview with Le'Veon Bell (49:00) which you can watch on CBS Sports HQ soon.
